Global Automation and Control Market

Automation and control market is expected to grow at a compound annual growth rate of 10.10% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on automation and control provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecasted period while providing their impacts on the marketâ€™s growth.

Automation and control allow manufacturing facilities to enhance the product quality and raise quantity and dependability while dropping the costs incurred in the production and designing of the product. It engrosses the use of control systems and logical programming commands to hold machines and industrial processes, thus reducing human intrusion.

The increasing demand for automation and control in the robotics industry with developments in artificial intelligence have been directly influencing the growth of automation and control market over the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Also the high adoption of industry 4.0 across various industries is also flourishing the growth of the automation and control market. Also with the help of automation, the various companies are considerably reducing labor and operational expenses and are also minimizing human errors due to the system consistency and efficiency which is also positively impacting the growth of the market. Furthermore, the rising adoption of industrial robots in the manufacturing industry in order to provide demand of increasing population is also acting as an active growth driver towards the growth of the automation and control market. However, rapidly changing technological trends in the manufacturing industry as well as various issues such as high implementation costs of the automation systems along with privacy and security concerns are acting as the major limitations for the growth of automation and control in the above mentioned forecasted period, whereas the lack of regulations and standards pertaining to industry 4.0 have the potential to challenge the automation and control market growth in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

Likewise, the rising adoption of process automation across various industries such as energy utilities, automotive and chemicals will further cater ample new opportunities that will lead to the growth of the automation and control market in the above mentioned forecasted period.

